<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The Wind Druid is a relatively strong and safe build that can clear out a large portion of the zones in Diablo 2 without much fear. He does not require a ton of gear but getting a couple of key Items can really help accelerate his farming speed and keep him safe from harm.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Wind Druid. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Hurricane@@@ - Main crowd control and cold Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Tornado@@@ - Main Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Twister@@@ - Prerequisite to @@@D2Tornado@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2CycloneArmor@@@ - Great Elemental Absorb, required</li>
<li>1-20 points to @@@D2OakSage@@@ - Bonus to Life for you and party, required</li>
</ol>

